  <brief_title>Dose Defining Study for the Administration of Vitamin K2 Supplements in Hemodialysis Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Prospective Open Interventional Multi-centre Study on Finding the Optimal Dose of Vitamin K2 Supplements for Hemodialysis Patients</official_title>
